	   <tr><td colspan=2>Agility doesn't drastically decrease the damage inflicted on you, according to most end game players.&nbsp;&nbsp;Although it does add 1 AC per couple of agi, adding agility is not quite efficient as adding pure ac.   However, in some cases that you may need some agility so that when you are overloaded or low on health, your agility don't drop below the penalty level.  This mean that you need some agility but not alot.    Of course, this precludes some classes whom their skills are based on agility.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
